==English==
===Noun===
'''tosser'''

# (''Mainly British slang'') Someone who masturbates. A [[wanker]].
# (''Mainly British slang'') Someone the speaker doesn't like ('that bloke what ripped me off was a right tosser')
Tosser, whilst carrying a heavy meaning is a less sociably un-acceptable form [[wanker]]. Whereas you would not use that word to describe someone in a conversation with your mother, "tosser" might be offered.
